Value: Way 2 Vat Limited, a technology company, provides value added tax (VAT), and goods and services tax (GST) reclaim solution in Israel and internationally. It develops the W2V Platform, a web application for reclaiming various types of VAT in various industries and markets. It offers foreign VAT/GST reclaim on account payable invoices; VAT/GST reclaim for local business travel; and foreign VAT/GST reclaim for companies. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Tel Aviv, Israel.
